                <h1>HOW TO KNOW A FLOOD PRONE AREA</h1>
                <p>There are several visual signs that can indicate that you live in a flood-prone area. Here are a few to look out for:</p>

                <h1></h1>
                <div class="scrollable">
                    <table>
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Cause </th>
